<paragraphs xml:id="expanding-our-library-of-functions">
<title>Expanding our library of functions</title>

<p> So far we have focused on polynomials (lines,
quadratics, cubics, and so on), exponential and logarithmic functions,
and sums, products, ratios. and compositions build from these.<!--
linebreak -->To better understand these functions and few new ones, we
compare their behaviors for large inputs.
</p>

</paragraphs>

